text: Rushden & Diamonds F.C. was a football club which played in Irthlingborough, England. The club was formed in 1992, when Rushden Town and Irthlingborough Diamonds merged. They were liquidated in 2011, and the fans decided to form a new club called AFC Rushden & Diamonds. == League position == Season League Position 2000/01 Conference Champions 2001/02 Third Division 6th 2002/03 Third Division Champions 2003/04 Second Division 22nd 2004/05 League Two 22nd 2005/06 League Two 24th 2006/07 Conference 12th / National 2007/08 Conference 16th / National 2008/09 Conference 11th / National Category:English football clubs Category:1992 establishments in England
